.landing-connect
  .container
    .text-center
      %img{src: '/img/ollert-logo-white.svg', width: '360px'}
    .h1{class: "text-center"}
      Learn what your Trello boards aren't telling you.
    .row{class: "text-center", style: 'margin-top: 40px;'}
      %a{class: "btn btn-primary btn-xl connect-btn", href: "javascript:void(0)", onClick: "#{@user.nil? ? 'TrelloController.authorizeAnonymous()' : 'TrelloController.authorizeUser()'}"}
        Connect to Get Started
.landing-info.landing-section
  .container
    .row.text-center.h1
      Why Ollert?

    .row.text-center.h3
      .col-md-3
        Your Trello boards do a great job telling you the state of today.
      .col-md-offset-1.col-md-4
        But how do you know what's happened during the past week, month, or year?
      .col-md-offset-1.col-md-3
        That's where Ollert comes in.
    .row
      .col-md-3
        %img{src: '/img/landing-trello.png', style: 'width: 100%;'}
      .col-md-offset-1.col-md-4.text-center
        %img{src: '/img/landing-question.png', style: 'width: 75%;'}
      .col-md-offset-1.col-md-3
        %img{src: '/img/landing-ollert.png', style: 'width: 100%;'}

.landing-victory.landing-section
  .container
    .row.text-center.h1
      A new way to think about Trello boards.

    .row.text-center.h3
      .col-md-5
        Use Ollert to visualize the progress of your boards.
      .col-md-offset-2.col-md-5
        Instantly see the numbers behind the cards.
    .row
      .col-md-5
        %img{src: '/img/landing-visualize.png', style: 'width: 100%;'}
      .col-md-offset-2.col-md-5
        %img{src: '/img/landing-instantly.png', style: 'width: 100%;'}

.landing-hook.landing-section
  .container
    .row.h1.text-center{style: 'margin-bottom: 20px;'}
      What are you waiting for? It's free.
    .row.text-center
      .col-md-offset-2.col-md-3
        %a{class: "btn btn-primary btn-xl", href: "javascript:void(0)", onClick: "#{@user.nil? ? 'TrelloController.authorizeAnonymous()' : 'TrelloController.authorizeUser()'}"}
          Get Started Now
      .col-md-offset-2.col-md-3
        %a{class: "btn btn-primary btn-xl", href: "/signup"}
          Create an Account
    .row.text-center.h4
      .col-md-offset-2.col-md-3
        Connect to Trello, choose a board, and view your stats. No strings attached.
      .col-md-offset-2.col-md-3
        Just supply an email and password. We'll remember your Trello information after the first time you authenticate. More benefits coming soon.
    .row.h2.text-center
      .small.text-center{style: 'margin-top: 10px;'}
        Want more information? Contact <a href="mailto:connect@ollertapp.com">connect@ollertapp.com</a>.

%script{src: "/js/flash-message.js"}